		"Jim can not read
	]em
	" is a game demo made by Verysoftwares that is currently in development. It presumably follows Jimi, who must acquire letters of the alphabet in order to clear textboxes and escape I guess.
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	"This movie aims to softlock a savefile (as in create a savefile that is impossible to complete, and it accomplishes that goal in just 17 seconds).
	$LF
]div
